<!-- SC_OFF --><div class="md"><p>Consider the common scenario of the same file in two panes (<code>C-x C-f</code> file, then <code>C-x 2</code>). One often references the top pane while actively editing the bottom pane. If you <code>C-x b</code> the bottom pane, say to consult another source, which buffer would you prefer as the default upon a subsequent <code>C-x b RET</code>?</p> <p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/poll/wmm50u">View Poll</a></p> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/nnreddit-user"> /u/nnreddit-user </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/emacs/comments/wmm50u/poll_switch_back_to_a_visible_buffer/">[link]</a></span> &#32; <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/emacs/comments/wmm50u/poll_switch_back_to_a_visible_buffer/">[comments]</a></span>